{
  "stem": "3855.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And that was unfortunately the problem with my parents, because they were both born in what was at the time-- mind you, not what the monarchy was-- what was at the time Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And as I say, as the climate changed, we took a whole different-- we started to take a different outlook.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'38.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe '37 we started to think about what's going on in Germany, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the real thrust to do something came only after Hitler marched into Austria.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It can't happen here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Let me phrase it this way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I think it could happen here, if you ask me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Here, meaning here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Austria?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They did not come to-- openly to political power, because the regime was Catholic-influenced, particularly just before.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was the famous Dollfuss.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was Schuschnigg, who in his last radio speech, vehemently spoke against the Nazis and terminated by saying, not-- finished the speech by saying, God save Austria.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So basically, these people came out of the woodwork immediately upon the Anschluss.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To give you an example, we had a mathematics teacher, Professor [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Hueba ?] in gymnasium, who was the most wonderful guy, really.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as soon as the Anschluss came, his brother became minister of justice [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] under the new regime.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this is how it went throughout.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People from-- the amazing part is, the university people, who the average person would assume know more than the guy on the street, are the ones who embraced this completely.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were totally mesmerized.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mesmerized.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were totally mesmerized by this powerful speaker who was able, like any great leader-- let's be honest, Roosevelt was able to convince the people that he is the man of the century.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In Hitler's case, the man of the millennium.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
